node.title: Police searching for missing 12yo Lower Hutt boy
node.description: Dylan Pickett was last seen on Saturday afternoon.
node.content: ["Police are urging New Zealanders to help them find a missing Lower Hutt boy.", "Dylan Pickett, 12, has been missing from his home since Saturday afternoon and his family says this is out of character.", "Police say he was last seen in Colson St, Avalon, at about 4pm and was walking towards Wingate Bridge. He was wearing a black hoodie with \"HERO\" written across the front, a Minecraft T-shirt, and cargo pants that are either black and white or brown and white.", "Dylan is of thin build and is 161cm tall.", "\"Police and his family have concerns for his welfare and ask anyone who has seen him to call Lower Hutt Police on 105 and refer to job number 220102/2177,\" police say."]
